					.d-flex.mt-5.align-items-top
						img.img-sm.rounded-circle.mr-3(src='/img/faces/face3.jpg', alt='image')
						.mb-0.flex-grow
							p.font-weight-bold.mr-2.mb-0 Jack Manque
							p
								| This is amazing! We have moved to a brand new office in
								| New Hampshire with a lot more space.
								| We will miss our old office but we are very excited about our new space.
						.ml-auto
							i.mdi.mdi-heart-outline.text-muted
